=== Another PHP Blog's Planetarium ===

This project aims to create an easy to install Blog planetarium in PHP.


=== How to install ===

+ Edit config.php
+ Create mysql database
    echo create database DBNAME | mysql -u USER
    cat  mysql-dump.sql | mysql -u USER DBNAME
    rm mysql-dump.sql
+ Crawling
    Execute scripts/crawl.php via web or any other crond task (recommended). 

